Title : Bjørn Gjevik
Text : '''Bjørn Gjevik''' (born 30 March 1939) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] physicist.

He hails from [[Hitra]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Med havet som forskningsfelt|work=Aftenposten|date=30 March 1989|page=14|author=A.K.|language=Norwegian}}</ref> He took the [[dr.philos.]] degree in 1972 and became a professor of [[hydrodynamics]] at the [[University of Oslo]] in 1977.<ref name=snl>{{cite encyclopedia|year=|title=Bjørn Gjevik|encyclopedia=[[Store norske leksikon]]|editor=|publisher=|location=|url=http://snl.no/Bj%C3%B8rn_Gjevik|language=Norwegian|accessdate=4 May 2014}}</ref> He is a fellow of the [[Norwegian Academy of Science and Letters]].<ref name=ntb>{{cite news|title=70 år 30. mars: Professor Bjørn Gjevik|agency=Norwegian News Agency|date=11 March 2009|language=Norwegian}}</ref>

He resides at [[Grav, Norway|Grav]].<ref name=ntb/>

